  	<h1>Hood to Coast&nbsp;2016 </h1>
  	<p class="intro">This year I had the pleasure of running at the <a href="http://www.hoodtocoastrelay.com/" target="_blank">Portland Hood to Coast relay</a>. I was lucky to join the <a href="http://www.north.com/" target="_blank">North</a>/<a href="http://uncorkedstudios.com/" target="_blank">Uncorked Studios</a> team with another 11 runners on two vans. We each ran 3 legs for a total of 199 miles in a little over 24hs. I was runner #11 on van #2 and I ran legs #11, #23, and #35.</p>
    
